#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:2
msgid "Vector creation"
msgstr "Kreiranje vektora"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:15
msgid "Array of offset (parallel) lines"
msgstr "Niz odmaknutih (paralelnih) linija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:16
msgid ""
"Creates copies of line features in a layer, by creating multiple offset "
"versions of each feature. Each new version is incrementally offset by a "
"specified distance."
msgstr ""
"Pravi kopije linijskih objekata u sloju tako što za svaki objekat kreira "
"više odmaknutih verzija. Svaka nova verzija odmaknuta je za zadato "
"rastojanje više od prethodne."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:20
msgid ""
"Positive distance will offset lines to the left, and negative distances will"
" offset them to the right."
msgstr "Pozitivno rastojanje odmiče linije ulevo, a negativno udesno."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:26
msgid "In blue the source layer, in red the offset one"
msgstr "Plavo je izvorni sloj, crveno odmaknuti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:28
msgid ""
"|checkbox| Allows :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` of line features"
msgstr ""
"|checkbox| Omogućava :ref:`izmenu objekata na licu mesta "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` za linijske objekte"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:2043
msgid "checkbox"
msgstr "checkbox"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:32
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:183
