#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:942
msgid ""
"Field or expression providing the order to connect the points in the path. "
"If not set, the feature ID (``$id``) is used."
msgstr ""
"Polje ili izraz koji daje redosled povezivanja tačaka u putanji. Ako se ne "
"postavi, koristi se ID objekta (``$id``)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:944
msgid "**Sort text containing numbers naturally**"
msgstr "**Sortiraj tekst sa brojevima prirodno**"

