"Specify the resulting point layer of pixels centroids. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte rezultujući tačkasti sloj centroida piksela. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1840
msgid "Resulting point layer with pixels centroids"
msgstr "Rezultujući tačkasti sloj sa centroidima piksela"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1845
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:pixelstopoints``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:pixelstopoints``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1855
msgid "Raster pixels to polygons"
msgstr "Pikseli rastera u poligone"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1856
msgid ""
"Creates a vector layer of polygons corresponding to each pixel in a raster "
"layer."
msgstr ""
"Pravi vektorski sloj poligona koji odgovaraju svakom pikselu rasterskog "
"sloja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1859
msgid ""
"Converts a raster layer to a vector layer, by creating polygon features for "
"each individual pixel's extent in the raster layer. Any NoData  pixels are "
"skipped in the output."
msgstr ""
"Pretvara rasterski sloj u vektorski tako što pravi poligonske objekte za "
"obuhvat svakog pojedinačnog piksela rasterskog sloja. Pikseli sa NoData  "
"preskaču se u izlazu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1889
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1913
msgid "**Vector polygons**"
msgstr "**Vektorski poligoni**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1894
msgid ""
"Specify the resulting polygon layer of pixel extents. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte rezultujući poligonski sloj obuhvata piksela. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1916
msgid "Resulting polygon layer of pixel extents"
msgstr "Rezultujući poligonski sloj obuhvata piksela"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1921
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:pixelstopolygons``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:pixelstopolygons``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1931
msgid "Regular points"
msgstr "Pravilne tačke"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1932
msgid ""
"Creates a new point layer with its points placed in a regular grid within a "
"given extent."
msgstr ""
"Pravi novi tačkasti sloj čije su tačke raspoređene u pravilnu mrežu unutar "
"zadatog obuhvata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1935
msgid ""
"The grid is specified either by the spacing between the points (same spacing"
" for all dimensions) or by the number of points to generate. In the latter "
"case, the spacing will be determined from the extent. In order to generate a"
" full rectangular grid, at least the number of points specified by the user "
"is generated for the latter case."
msgstr ""
"Mreža se zadaje razmakom između tačaka (isti razmak za sve dimenzije) ili "
"brojem tačaka koje se generišu. U drugom slučaju, razmak se određuje iz "
"obuhvata. Da bi se generisala puna pravougaona mreža, u drugom slučaju "
"generiše se najmanje onoliko tačaka koliko je korisnik zadao."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1941
msgid ""
"Random offsets to the point spacing can be applied, resulting in a non-"
"regular point pattern."
msgstr ""
"Na razmak tačaka mogu se primeniti slučajni pomeraji, što daje nepravilan "
"raspored tačaka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1958
msgid "**Input extent (xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax)**"
msgstr "**Ulazni obuhvat (xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1967
msgid "**Point spacing/count**"
msgstr "**Razmak/broj tačaka**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1968
msgid "``SPACING``"
msgstr "``SPACING``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1971
msgid "Default: 100"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 100"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1972
msgid ""
"Spacing between the points, or the number of points, depending on whether "
"``Use point spacing`` is checked or not."
msgstr ""
"Razmak između tačaka ili broj tačaka, u zavisnosti od toga da li je ``Use "
"point spacing`` označeno ili nije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1974
msgid "**Initial inset from corner (LH side)**"
msgstr "**Početno uvlačenje od ugla (leva strana)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1975
msgid "``INSET``"
msgstr "``INSET``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1979
msgid ""
"Offsets the points relative to the upper left corner. The value is used for "
"both the X and Y axis."
msgstr ""
"Pomera tačke u odnosu na gornji levi ugao. Vrednost se koristi i za X i za Y"
" osu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1981
msgid "**Apply random offset to point spacing**"
msgstr "**Primeni slučajni pomeraj na razmak tačaka**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1982
msgid "``RANDOMIZE``"
msgstr "``RANDOMIZE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1986
msgid "If checked the points will have a random spacing"
msgstr "Ako je označeno, tačke će imati slučajan razmak"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1987
msgid "**Use point spacing**"
msgstr "**Koristi razmak tačaka**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1988
msgid "``IS_SPACING``"
msgstr "``IS_SPACING``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1992
msgid "If unchecked the point spacing is not taken into account"
msgstr "Ako nije označeno, razmak tačaka se ne uzima u obzir"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1993
msgid "**Output layer CRS**"
msgstr "**CRS izlaznog sloja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1999
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:2022
msgid "**Regular points**"
msgstr "**Pravilne tačke**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:2004
msgid ""
"Specify the output regular point layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni sloj pravilnih tačaka. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:2025
msgid "The output regular point layer."
msgstr "Izlazni sloj pravilnih tačaka."

